data.description: Welcome to 1609 Falmouth Way, a move-in ready single-family home that combines comfort, style and convenience in the heart of Modesto, California. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence provides a serene escape in a quiet, established neighborhood with all the amenities you need. Once you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting living area with stained concrete floors and BRAND NEW vinyl waterproof plank floors in the hallways. The kitchen provides plenty of storage space and stylish granite countertops. The home features three comfortable bedrooms each with its own unique charm. The master suite provides a private retreat with an en-suite bathroom for your convenience. 1609 Falmouth Way is situated in a peaceful neighborhood near schools, shopping, dining and local parks. This home is perfect for first-time home buyers, growing families or anyone seeking a tranquil place to call home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and convenience this property has to offer.
